description:
This is a 22 minute workout called 'Beginner At Home Calisthenics Workout - No Equipment, 20 Minutes, Full Body' from the channel Lucy Lismore.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
